            <h2>üåÄ The Founders of Konoha</h2>
            <img src="c:\Users\Lenovo\Downloads\madara-uchiha-vs-hashirama-senju.jpg" alt="Hashirama and Madara">
            <p><strong> Hashirama Senju & Madara Uchiha</strong></p>
            <p>Konohagakure was founded by *Hashirama Senju* and *Madara Uchiha*, two of the most powerful shinobi in history. Hashirama, known as the "God of Shinobi," sought peace and unity among ninja clans, while Madara, a fierce warrior from the Uchiha clan, had a different vision for the village's leadership.</p>
            <p>Their rivalry shaped the foundation of Konoha, culminating in a legendary battle at the Valley of the End. Despite their differences, their ideals continued to influence the village's future generations, shaping its destiny through war and peace.</p>
