            <h2>üêçüê∏üêå The Legendary Sannin of Konoha</h2>
            <img src="c:\Users\Lenovo\Downloads\sanins.webp" alt="Legendary Sannin">
            <p><strong> Jiraiya, Tsunade & Orochimaru</strong></p>
            <p>The *Legendary Sannin* ‚Äì Jiraiya, Tsunade, and Orochimaru ‚Äì were the students of the Third Hokage, Hiruzen Sarutobi. Each of them became famous for their unique skills and contributions to the ninja world:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Jiraiya:</strong> A legendary ninja known for his research on ninjutsu and his mastery of Sage Mode. He was the mentor of Naruto Uzumaki and an expert in summoning toads.</li>
                <li><strong>Tsunade:</strong> The greatest medical-nin in history and the Fifth Hokage of Konoha. She possesses immense strength and pioneered modern medical ninjutsu.</li>
                <li><strong>Orochimaru:</strong> A genius scientist and master of forbidden jutsu, known for his obsession with immortality and experimentation on humans.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Together, these three shinobi played a crucial role in shaping the destiny of Konoha and the ninja world.</p>
